STEPS: 

1: Build the Ultimate staffs 

2: Go into the giants heads and place the staffs. Thor = Lightning Odin = Wind Freya = Frost and the Fire staff goes onto a stand inside of the main escavation site. 

3: You must build the Odin Strike, or the beacon (whatever you call it). One person needs to go inside of a robot and the other stand outside of the seal (concrete) near the outside of the map near stamina-up. Throw the beacon and activate the giant's firing sequence and it will break open the concrete. 

4: Use the Maxis drone near the broken seal to activate the Panzer Soldat's to spawn in (Warning 8) 

5: Go into the blood mode and shoot down the red plane. After shot down, go into blood mode again and shoot the pilot . He is found circleing the escavation site outside and looks like a regular zombie & ONLY TAKEO CAN DO THIS STEP!

6: You must have the Kung Fu Hands for this (you get them from getting the odin bomb). Go to the bottom of the escavation site and kill the zombies with the white mist surrounding their hands with your fists. After doing too many, you will pick up the ultimate hands, which are related to your elements. If you have fire, you now punch fire. (Sweet as hell). 

7: Go into the crazy place and kill a TON of zombies. it will create a giant electric whisp above your head and then will open up the void between the crazy place and the real world. You get the achievement here. 

8: Get the maxis drone and use it in the crazy place and the game ends to reveal the final cutscene !

MpVMVXmBXIY.title: 2 Corner Store Lane, Ocean City Maryland Rental
MpVMVXmBXIY.description:
Features:

    * 5 Bedrooms, 3.5 Baths
    * Ocean City's Premier Luxury Community
    * Amenity Filled Resort Area With General Store
    * Indoor & Outdoor Pools Plus Private Beaches
    * Clubhouse With Fitness Center
    * Off-Season Mini-Weeks & Extended Weekends Available At Discounted Pricing - Please Inquire!

Remarks:
The home is a 5 bedroom home in the sense that there are 4 bedrooms with a bed and a closet. The 5th bedroom has a futon in it and a closet across the hall from it and there is also a queen sofa pull-out bed in the family room.

The bedrooms are as follows:

1 master bedroom with a king bed and private full bathroom with double sinks, a shower and a soaking tub,

1 loft bedroom with a king bed and private full bathroom with a single sink and a shower,

2 bedrooms with a queen bed that share a full bathroom with a single sink and a shower/tub combo in the hall,

1 bedroom with a futon day bed on the first floor,

1 queen sofa pull-out bed in the family room.

In addition, there are 2 half bathrooms in the house; one on the first floor and one on the second floor. The townhome has 4 levels.

Sunset Island is a private, gated 37-acre island community on Ocean City, Maryland's bayside at 67th Street with private beaches, pools, shopping, fishing, boat marina and more.

The community offers the best of all worlds: exclusive bayside vacation rental homes with boat slips that are only two blocks from the Atlantic Ocean. Combine the water, beaches, beach café and newly opened corner store and you'll never have to leave the island during your vacation retreat!

This townhome has multiple porches, decks, and the private loft balcony is perfect for watching sunsets over the bay. This townhome is fully equipped with new furnishings, appliances, tile flooring, flat-panel cable televisions, DVD players, a 50" plasma HD TV and washer & dryer.

With over 2,500 square feet of living space, this 5 bedroom, 3.5.5 bathroom townhouse is a perfect vacation retreat! The entry level features a private study/bedroom with french doors. The laundry room is conveniently located on the entry level and an outdoor shower is included.

The second floor features an enormous great room, a powder room, an oversized gourmet kitchen, and a dramatic morning room. The third level features a luxurious owner's suite with a soaking tub, separate shower, double-bowl vanity and walk-in closet. Two additional bedrooms and a full bath complete the third level. The fourth level loft includes a private sundeck, full bath and walk-in closet.

The townhome features a two car garage as well as a parking pad for two more cars.

IAr1lyscIko.title: DBZ BT3 Majin Vegeta Vs Red Potara Majin Buu
IAr1lyscIko.description:
Majin Vegeta Takes On another Majin Buu, only this one is 1o times more powerful.Can Vegeta Stop Majin Buu even with 7 magical red potaras?


Red Potara/God Characters are password characters that are equipped with 7 red potaras (Z-Items) which you can't unlock in the game.

They have:
-An extra 30,000 Health
-All stats +3
-Sturdy Body (won't be easily stunned)
-Will also easily stun opponents
-Guard Crushes remove a huge amount of Ki
-Also, can't be Guard Crushed
-Health and Ki are slowly recovered
-Ki charges ultra fast
-All 4 power ups
-Vanish Attack/Dragon Homing +2
-Blast 1 costs -1
-Blast 2/UB/Ki Blasts costs half
-Various movements will cost no Ki at all (Dragon Dashes, for instance)
-Movements whose costs aren't nullified will only cost half Ki
-Auto Afterimage while in Max Power
-Takes no damage while guarding
-Gains huge advantage in Clashes

Dayz Standalone has just been announced for PlayStation 4 (PS4) at Gamescom 2014! There will most likely be more platforms to follow.

Enjoyed the video? Subscribe: http://bit.ly/Uz4Up9

Dayz started as a mod back in 2012 and was later released as a standalone game. It started on Arma 2, and then it used a modified engine from Take On Helicopters made by Bohemia Interactive. The creator of Dayz is Dean Hall and he now works with Bohemia Interactive as the lead for Dayz (for the remainder of the year). It is the zombie survival sandbox genre.

Dayz being announced for the PS4 caused a lot of arguments. Dean Hall announced it would arrive to the Playstation 4 in the next 3 years. He also stated on Reddit that it will most likely arrive on other platforms such as Linux and Xbox. Development for Dayz on PC will not be halted, as they are having a separate team work on the console version.

首猫背を改善する肩甲骨ストレッチ
廣井整体院HP　→　https://hiroiseitai.com/

首猫背とは簡単に言うと首（頸椎）と背中（胸椎）の境目あたりから首が折れ曲がってしまっているような状態のことを言います。

では、首猫背を改善する肩甲骨ストレッチをご紹介していきたいと思います。

まず手を、胸を張った状態から腕を９０度に曲げて手を上方向に向けます。

この状態から胸を張って背中を伸ばした状態のまま、ゆっくりと真横に腕が耳に付くまで上げていきます。

この時は顎が上がって前に出てしまわないように顎を前に引いておこないます。

ゆっくりと腕を上げていって腕が耳につくところまでいってゆっくり下ろす。

こうしたら今度は左右に上半身を捻っていきます。今度は左ですね。

今度は腕を外方向に捻っていきます。

捻ったら戻す。

この一連の動作、戻して左右ですね。外に捻る。

これを１セットとして、５セットおこなってください。

次に正座をした状態から腕を後ろで組みます。

顎を引いて胸を張って後ろで組んだ腕と肘を伸ばします。

腕と肘を伸ばした状態から腕をゆっくりと上方向に持ち上げていきます。

この時に体が、上半身が前に倒れたりしないように背中をしっかりと伸ばした状態で顎を引いておきます。

いっぱいまで上がるところまで上げてこの状態を２０秒キープします。

キープしてもらったら一旦腕を下ろして少し休憩してまた上げる。

これを３セットおこなってもらいます。

首猫背の状態になると背中にある肩甲骨の動きが非常に悪くなっているので、この肩甲骨ストレッチを継続的におこなってもらうことで肩甲骨周りの筋肉の動きが良くなると首猫背の改善にも繋がるのでぜひお試しください。

以上が首猫背を改善する肩甲骨ストレッチでした。

2vPKjFYIJyE.title: DJI Phantom FPV with Carbon Fiber Props (6/2/13)
2vPKjFYIJyE.description:
(*High Altitude Tests) My first flight with the carbon fiber propellers. I was using a combination of line of sight and a 10" portable LCD. I managed to get up to 400 feet (at 3:10), and the view was spectacular! The up/down that you see in the video was me testing the gimbal's axis.

Filmed at Maximo Park (St. Petersburg, FL)

Pros:
Lot's of power and speed
They won't break or snap off during hard flying
Sound and look great!

Cons:
Setting the gains is tricky...it's hard to get rid of the wobble
The Phantom seems to drift a lot more
Must use strong thread-lock liquid (if you want to keep the default prop nuts)
VERY DANGEROUS! The Phantom ends up becoming a flying chainsaw!

Verdict: I think I'll stick with the DJI black props...don't get me wrong, the carbon fiber ones are slick, but I don't like the tradeoffs (unless I can perfect the gains to be a lot more stable).
